Class ETagAssertionCTSOptionFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.cts.impl.ETagAssertionCTSOptionFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LdapOptionFunction

    public class ETagAssertionCTSOptionFunction
extends Object
implements LdapOptionFunction
    Function that is invoked for the CTSOptions.OPTIMISTIC_CONCURRENCY_CHECK_OPTION.

    If the Options contains a non-null etag value then the AssertionRequestControl will be added to the request.
